      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Audio and Visual Materials</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Audio and Visual Materials series (1.0 linear feet and 1 outsize film) is divided into three subseries: Photographs, Audiotapes, and Films.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <c02 level="subseries">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Photographs</unittitle>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>The Photographs are from a wide range of years (late 1800s to 1979) and portray former faculty and staff and facilities. Additional photographs of European physiologists collected by Dr. Lombard are located in one folder in the outsize box.</p>
          </scopecontent>
